text: Juan González (born 21 September 1972) is an Andorran former cyclist. He competed in the individual road race at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Andorran male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Andorra Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
